to be sexy.

130
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,500
Yes.

131
00:07:34,633 --> 00:07:36,733
You're so thick-faced!

132
00:07:36,867 --> 00:07:37,967
That's our food.

133
00:07:39,733 --> 00:07:41,000
What's happening here?

134
00:07:41,133 --> 00:07:42,167
Just relax, it's early.

135
00:07:42,300 --> 00:07:45,733
That's because look,
they've taken our food.

136
00:07:45,867 --> 00:07:47,867
That's okay, Grandmother
I'm not hungry yet.

137
00:07:48,033 --> 00:07:48,667
Okay, just eat.

138
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:50,433
Okay.

139
00:07:50,567 --> 00:07:51,200
Kalamansi, do you want it?

140
00:07:51,333 --> 00:07:52,067
- It's all yours.
- Catch.

141
00:07:52,833 --> 00:07:53,667
Oh by the way,

142
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,233
what's your plan for the
investigation now

143
00:07:55,367 --> 00:07:58,300
