the flak.

430
00:24:26,033 --> 00:24:27,000
Is that impressive?

431
00:24:27,133 --> 00:24:29,633
This might be the turning point
of your life.

432
00:24:29,800 --> 00:24:32,833
Make sure you make
the right decision.

433
00:24:32,967 --> 00:24:35,733
What if I slit your neck
so you'll take me seriously?

434
00:24:35,867 --> 00:24:37,167
I don't feel that way, Amo.

435
00:24:37,300 --> 00:24:39,533
There's already been a rumor,
that a child was abandoned?

436
00:24:39,667 --> 00:24:43,667
A picture of us at Lara's
funeral.

437
00:24:43,800 --> 00:24:45,533
Why do they look so much alike?

438
00:24:45,667 --> 00:24:46,967
Are they related?
